the face of love is a 2013 american romantic drama film directed by &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; posin and co-written by matthew mcduffie . the film stars annette bening , ed harris , robin williams , amy brenneman , jess weixler and linda park . it was screened in the special presentation section at the 2013 toronto international film festival . this was robin williams ' final role before his death in 2014 .